Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:07.37,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,When {\i0}Elder Tale{\i1} was a game, \None goal was to make
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:10.73,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the game world a one-half-scale model of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.55,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Half Gaia Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:16.65,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, the land corresponding to Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.56,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,is known as the Crescent Islands of Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:24.63,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The northernmost area of \Nwhich is the Ezzo Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Brigandia's the guild that's bossing \Npeople around in Susukino, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.65,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even when this was a game, \Nthey had a bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.23,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,To them, this world must be heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:15.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.24,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Marie will talk to Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.29,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:23.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But, my lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we meeting them in the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.79,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is it unsafe outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:33.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If we meet up outside and \Nare wiped out in a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,we'd revive in the Akihabara Cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:40.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,but Serara would revive at \Nthe Susukino Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Serara is on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.29,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,a Brigandia member's Friend List, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:54.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Her current hiding spot is within a \Nprivate zone, so they can't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:03:00.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But the minute she leaves, \Nthey'll locate her and send pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.02,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So she's gotta get out before they catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:07.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, I'd like you to hide yourself \Nwith Sneak and Silent Move, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:08.75,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No "please," my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:18.65,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sneak enables self-concealment, while \NSilent Move allows motion without any sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.13,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They're tracker-class skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's get this plan in gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:31.02,Title1,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1606,1)}Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.38,Default - margin,S,0000,0000,0000,,Escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.71,HUD1,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Location Search
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:33.65,HUD1,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Location Search \N\NTarget Not Within Specified Area
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:37.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you hiding, Serara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going \Nto obsess over that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta keep a tight lead on your pets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let them know who's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Demikas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:51.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.80,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Two guys you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They appear to be outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.72,HUD1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Displaying Serara's location
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.29,HUD1,{Friend,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Displaying Serara's location \NSusukino: Corridors of Time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they noticed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:07.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:11.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, talk about a nasty atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:25.65,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:32.41,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:38.96,HUD Big,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Serara \N{\fs24}\NRace/ Human\NDruid, Lv. 19
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.59,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Serara, of the Crescent Moon Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.81,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.71,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:45.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:57.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... If it isn't little Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:02.82,HUD Big,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta \N{\fs24}Race/ Cat-man\NSwashbuckler, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:02.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That explains how you arrived so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.82,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.95,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,He's a very smart kid, and a very good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:20.25,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,If he's here, our plan is sure to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:24.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see you still meow all the time, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.01,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:30.14,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,This is the correct way for cat people to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.14,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.39,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:39.50,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Little Shiroe used to check me for fleas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.74,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I can go back to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.29,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Nyanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And one other, a girl named Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A level-90 assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.67,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then little Naotsugu's here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.07,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And a new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:09.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be best if \Nyou came with us, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.59,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:17.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it is a sign from above, \Ntelling me to go to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.60,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.95,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.33,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,On their way, they're searching the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But they're close enough to be here in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.65,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Their leader seems to be an \Nenormous martial artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monk, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:45.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bear carved out of wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.73,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That would be Brigandia's guild master, Demikas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:55.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:57.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.53,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.23,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:01.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take the rear exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Londark...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.23,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.51,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,So the outsiders really were here for Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.74,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,The transport gate is shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.83,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.59,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They won't attack yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting isn't allowed within towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:41.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They'll wait until we're outside to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.67,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then how will we escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:52.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If they're letting us leave, then we just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That makes things easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:58.26,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if we leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.68,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,They might attack us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not "might." They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:11.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're outside the no-PvP zone, \Ntheir plan is to surround and PK us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:16.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Their first priority will probably be \Nyour confederate, Chief Nyanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That will destroy your will and \Nput you under their control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost certain of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.02,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.96,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.45,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,They might kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.80,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.81,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Serara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:39.12,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave this to Shiroe, and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.17,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:46.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Serara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Nyanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.10,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you went one-on-one with \Nthe enemy leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.81,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,A foolish question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.81,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.99,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them touch you, Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:21.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Which of you is Brigandia's Demi-glace?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.78,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.98,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Asking something so loudly is rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.21,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I know which one he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:38.22,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's the excessively huge guy sitting over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.13,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Demikas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.85,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:54.40,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't think you could disobey \Nme and get away with it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.15,HUD Big,D,0000,0000,0000,,Londark \N{\fs24}{\fs24}Race/ Elf\NSorcerer, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.63,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,If you come back now, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:01.28,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll send you to the \NCathedral ten times first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.27,HUD Big,D,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Demikas \N{\fs24}Race/ Human\NMonk, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.46,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Recklessness is the way of the young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.49,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,And tolerance is the beauty of adulthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.17,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.38,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,There is such a thing as going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.95,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.71,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Reigning in children who stray too far
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the lines is also an adult's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:26.73,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I'll fight you one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.06,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.98,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I fight you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.90,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid to face me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt, Mister, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't have to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer the one in the gray robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:51.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that an artifact drop from \Nthe Fire Lizard's Cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You seem stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:58.13,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard my name, Londark of Gray Steel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So you have a nickname...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:01.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.61,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It would be more satisfying for both of us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the strongest fighters settled things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.01,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have our Chief Nyanta fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.02,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Let us finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:18.53,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,We can ignore the cowardly meatball here, \Nas he's too scared to fight himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.28,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to fight that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.33,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.30,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've gotten to devour someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.85,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:57.02,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather the lady didn't see anything too gory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.69,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to go easy, tell me quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:06.72,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Demikas is in the monk class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.87,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,One of the three warrior classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.21,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,alongside guardian and samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:20.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Many {\i0}Elder Tale {\i1}techniques have both{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:23.13,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,Status/ {\c&H5657A6&}In Combat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.12,SignC,,0000,0000,0000,,Techniques\N\NQuests
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:23.12,SignD,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment\N\NItems
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:25.46,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,what are known as cast times and cool down times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.78,SignC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)}Shadow Kick\N\NTiger Echo Fist \N\NAura Saber\N\NTriple Blow \N\NDual Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:34.17,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Cast time is how long it takes a \Nspell to have effect, once it's cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.57,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down time is how long it takes before
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.45,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,you can reuse a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:42.89,SignC,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Kick\N\NTiger Echo Fist \N\NAura Saber\N\NTriple Blow \N\NDual Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:45.49,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Aura Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:49.99,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Monk-class techniques have short cool downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.45,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They chain techniques, \Ngiving opponents no recovery time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.08,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Step!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:02.13,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could defeat me \Nwith those little toy swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.78,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.29,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,A rapier is a gentleman's weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.60,HUD Big,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}Demikas                                                 Nyanta
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.22,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta's hit points...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.14,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Demikas has more HP.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.83,HUD Big,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}Demikas                                                 Nyanta
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.63,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.32,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The swashbuckler...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:30.53,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the specialized weapon classes, \Nand one of the few that can dual wield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:37.31,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,What sets it apart are the bad statuses \Ntheir weapons can inflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:43.38,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Lowered attack, lowered dodge, \Nlowered defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.22,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They can negate an opponent's strengths...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:49.26,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Or worsen their weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.23,Default - italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it look like Demikas is losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:00.46,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Stop jumping around, and fight fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:06.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Coming from you, "fair and square" sounds \Nlike a bastardization of our fair language.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Serara...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When I give the signal, I want you to \Ncast a healing pulse on everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.29,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, heal me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:24.13,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Surround the cat and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.73,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.68,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anchor Howl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.48,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Healer teams, heal Demikas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.29,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:53.49,HUD Big,L,0000,0000,0000,,Demikas \N{\fs24}Race/ Human\NMonk, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:53.87,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.58,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Take out the guardian first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.35,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.39,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.58,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,No... They'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Heal everyone! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:06.88,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.14,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Heartbeat Healing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:18.76,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Druid is one of the healing classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.86,HUD Big,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta \N{\fs24}Race/ Cat-man\NSwashbuckler, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:24.45,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Once they cast a healing pulse on someone, \Nit remains in effect for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.48,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.90,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.19,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,My level isn't high enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about Naotsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on Nyanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.00,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But... They're both in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do something, then don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:45.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.68,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.27,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.61,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Must be hard to get by \Nwith one crappy healer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.81,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.78,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.41,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend, the warrior, is about to go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.40,HUD Big,D,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.52,HUD Big,D,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}Naotsugu                                        Nyanta
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:30.21,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.25,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Castle of Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.23,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,No damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.21,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Castle of Stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:51.07,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,This spell blocks all damage \Nfor a ten-second period.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.96,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,An emergency-defense skill \Nonly available to guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Cast all your healing spells on Naotsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:00.54,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.49,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Healing Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.29,HUD Big,D,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Naotsugu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:09.80,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Buying time won't save you, Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:13.09,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Castle of Stone has a ten-minute cool down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.29,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If he's using a skill he can't use \Nagain for another ten minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.14,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,that guardian must be out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.06,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,He must be starting to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:27.44,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,When the spell runs out, you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:31.75,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You've made this harder \Nthan it had to be, Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:37.57,HUD Big,D,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Serara                                    Naotsugu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.63,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.29,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Heal quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.24,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger Echo Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:44.08,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:48.09,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Think it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.18,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Chief Nyanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.51,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.84,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thorn Bind Hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.15,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,A root?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:08.86,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.93,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:35.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:43.97,HUD Big,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Demikas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:40.27,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,His entire HP vanished in an instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.39,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.82,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Healers, heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.12,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,We can still—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.63,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.86,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,A single attack
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:04.09,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,from a swashbuckler could never \Ndefeat a level-90 monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:08.31,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even an assassin, which boasts \Nthe highest attack power
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:11.38,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,among weapon-specialization \Nclasses, couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:16.26,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, the secret lies in my lord's spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:18.63,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thorn Bind Hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.62,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Those shining thorns deal 1,000 \Ndamage to the target
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.75,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,for each hit by an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.27,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying all five thorns does 5,000 damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:31.15,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the sword damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.44,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,that isn't enough to beat Demikas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:36.34,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Which probably means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.44,HUD Big,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs24}Monk, Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:40.78,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thorn Bind Hostage has a \Nfifteen-second cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.36,SignC,A,0000,0000,0000,,Electrical Fuzz \N\NThorn Bind Hostage (seconds left)\N\NCast on Beat\N\NSoul Weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:45.49,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,The swashbuckler waited fourteen \Nseconds to begin his attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.08,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,He hit nine times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.95,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,First five...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:56.30,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,One attack takes .22 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:20:00.01,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,And after he destroyed the fifth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:03.65,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,my lord recast the thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.72,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,And then he cut four...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.10,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.90,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.36,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But is it really possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:21.91,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,That must be why Naotsugu \Nused Castle of Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:24.16,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew this was their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:29.79,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,For them to work together that way, \Nwithout coordinating ahead of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:34.66,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I could not do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Put away your swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:45.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We came through the Depths of Palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:51.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara and this city are no longer so far \Napart as to prevent travel between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished causing this kind of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We've won this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:02.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you still want to fight, Demikas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.02,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.93,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you all to the Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:11.37,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Until you break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.68,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:25.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you're the one taking a trip to the Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.30,HUD Big,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe/ Adventurer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.30,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.62,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Enchanter Shiroe,
